    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Step into a time capsule of elegance and power. This isn't just a car; it's a preserved legacy draped in a deep, lustrous Midnight Blue that seems to swallow the moonlight. Inside, the scent of hand-stitched leather greets you like a familiar library, while the polished walnut trim glows with a warmth only decades of care can provide. As you turn the key, the engine awakens with a sophisticated growl\u2014a mechanical symphony that promises endless coastal drives and sunset horizons. Every curve of its silhouette tells a story of prestige and untamed spirit. To drive this machine is to command a masterpiece that has been waiting specifically for your touch.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
